"""Test get_ficon_emulation_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_ficon_emulation_stats(ficon_emulation_id=self.
    p_data.ficon_emu_id, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now, end_time
    =self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.FICON_EMU))
